query:
DELETE FROM initiatives WHERE id NOT IN (
  SELECT id FROM (
    SELECT id FROM initiatives WHERE 
      title LIKE '%Social Media%' OR 
      title LIKE '%Email Campaign%' OR 
      title LIKE '%Customer Lifetime Value%' OR 
      title LIKE '%Analytics Dashboard%' OR 
      title LIKE '%Image Enhancement%' OR 
      title LIKE '%Video Production%'
  ) AS keep_ids
);
